Intelligence System(Streaming)
=============================================
It is a continuous building platform at every instance of your life.It is resultant perception of every event cross in your life.
Each and every human learn/experience something little or more from the event/action/activity/feeling/understanding/observation..so on..occur/cross in their life.These experience continuously use in building the intelligence system.Your every activity gating touch little or more by already build Intelligence system.

Each and every human Intelligence system are capable to distinguish the situation either left or right. It can detect the situation always in two phase like....

-harmful/faithful,   -freedom/bounded
-right/wrong, -believe/leave
-good/bad, -go ahead/quit
-mine/yours, -like/not like
-light/dark, -beautiful/ugly
-illusion/reality, -testy/bitter
-fight/run away, -satisfy/not satisfy
-happy/sad or delight..
-so on..

Building Intelligence system(birth ..transformation)
------------------------------------------
At the very childhood sate of life everything is unaware, is there any meaning of anything? No.
As child grow it aware from the object/situation/event..so on at a light state of experience.This is nothing but the thin/light base/birth of intelligence system.
When child become young, at this state brain experience the object/event/action...so on and consolidate in two phase of their Intelligence system.
At this stage Intelligence system able to distinguish the stuff and try to touch the event/action/feeling/understanding/thought..so on.

Ex-
When one drink without knowing it is faithful/harmful, one experience nice and add it in their intelligence system.Next time before drink if one knew it is harmful for leaver, this knowledge get added  in their intelligence system. when they try to drink, before drink the  Intelligence system try to touch the current event/action as it is harmful too. 

When one have been gating energy continuously for many years, their observation power/the capability to detect known/unknown frequency/sensitivity/feeling/understanding..so on getting increase day by day. That means a poor intelligence system transformed to sensitive/rich intelligence system.
   
A rich/sensitive intelligence system never gives chance for suspicion on its Intelligence system to poor intelligence system.
A poor intelligence system have no capability to cross verify the observation/feeling/understanding of sensitive intelligence system. That means either poor intelligence system have to follow the rich intelligence system or not to rich in their frequency.
Poor intelligence system mostly get influence by sensitive intelligence system.A poor intelligence system never understand every intelligence system have unique capability and their is no any meaning to correlate with other intelligence system.
Every query of poor intelligence system can be satisfy by sensitive intelligence  system.

Ex-
-Scientists have rich intelligence system on their research than other human being.
-A Teacher have rich intelligence system than their student.
-Successful businessman have rich intelligence system towards business.
-Doctor have rich intelligence system to know the disease.
-Spiritual people have rich intelligence system towards living of life.
..so on..
 
***Rich intelligence system have a eye in front of poor intelligence system***

